{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "03", "m": "11", "Y": "2025"}, "time": {"H": "08", "M": "14", "S": "56"}}, "news": [{"title": "Land lease defaulters owe Kerala government \u20b9665 crore", "para": "The state has identified 584 individuals and organizations occupying government-leased land without paying dues or violating lease terms, accumulating arrears of Rs 665.30 crore. Despite significant financial dues, only a negligible amount of land has been reclaimed, and the government lacks a compiled record of total illegally occupied land.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/keralas-land-lease-violators-owe-government-665-crore/125046966?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-25108/125046966.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Bhubaneswar: 100 more flats handed over in third phase at Shantipalli Awas Yojana", "para": "Bhubaneswar Municipal Corporation and Bhubaneswar Development Authority have allotted over 100 more units at Shantipalli Awas Yojana, bringing the total beneficiaries to 560. This marks the third phase of allotment for Keshari Residency, one of three affordable housing projects under PM Awas Yojana in the city. The project, a public-private partnership, will eventually comprise 1,300 dwelling units.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/bhubaneswar-hands-over-100-flats-in-third-phase-of-shantipalli-awas-yojana/125046914?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-130996/125046914.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}, {"title": "HC directs Haryana government to explain delay in constituting SEIAA after February", "para": "The Punjab and Haryana High Court has ordered the State of Haryana to provide a specific affidavit. This affidavit must clarify why the State Environment Impact Assessment Authority has not been constituted after February 2025. The court also seeks all correspondence between the state and the Union government on this matter.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/high-court-orders-haryana-to-justify-delay-in-seiaa-formation-after-february-2025/125046566?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-11914/125046566.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}]}